Galatasaray, the Istanbul club who knocked  Manchester United of the European Cup, won the Turkish league on Sunday,  finishing a point clear of Fenerbahce after winning their last game.
Selected results
Trabzonspor 4 Sariyer 2
Galatasaray 2 Bursaspor 0
Karsiyaka 0 Fenerbahce 4
Final positions (after 30 matches)
Galatasaray 70pts, Fenerbahce 69, Trabzonspor 59, Besiktas 54, Samsunspor  50
